   <div class="content light hidden-phone">
    <h2 class="section-header">
     Hands-on, learn-by-doing training in months not years
    </h2>
    <h3 class="section-header">
     We've placed thousands in broadcast media
    </h3>
    <div class="row-fluid main-description">
     <div class="span6">
      <p>
       We're a broadcasting school that offers the hands-on training and industry connections you need to start a career in audio/video production, television, sports broadcasting, and radio. Our graduates have gone on to work at major employers in the broadcasting industry such as iHeartMedia, ESPN, CNN, CBS Radio, Fox, MSNBC, and SiriusXM - to name a few.
      </p>
     </div>
     <div class="span6">
      <p>
       We have twelve
       <a href="locations">
        broadcasting schools
       </a>
       along the east coast of the United States. Contact
       <a href="admissions">
        admissions
       </a>
       to learn more about becoming a student and get information about scholarships and financial assistance. In a few months you could be doing audio/video production work, working behind the scenes in television, having a ball on the field as a sports broadcaster or sitting down to your new career as a radio on-air personality!
      </p>
     </div>
