      <div style="background-image: none;" class="content light">
       <div class="row-fluid">
        <h2 style="text-align:center" class="inline-header">
         Here's what makes us different from other schools
        </h2>
       </div>
       <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Hands-On Training
         </h4>
         <p>
          From your first day of classes you'll be working with the equipment used by real radio and television professionals - not sitting in a classroom taking notes.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Small Class Sizes
         </h4>
         <p>
          Class sizes are deliberately small and our instructors give you personalized attention. Students love the team atmosphere and working on studio projects.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Instructors Work In The Industry
         </h4>
         <p>
          There's nothing better than learning from instructors who work in the broadcast industry. In many cases, your instructor could be your future employer!
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Use of Our Studios
         </h4>
         <p>
          Students are always welcome to use our studios. Stay on top of the ever-changing technology, work on your demo, or practice your on-air performance.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Alumni Network
         </h4>
         <p>
          As a graduate, you'll be welcomed into a family of professional broadcasters who can help you get ahead in your broadcasting career.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Scholarships Available
         </h4>
         <p>
          Leading companies in the brodcasting &amp; media industry offer scholarships to qualifed students. Contact us to get more information.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Get Trained in Months - Not Years
         </h4>
         <p>
          Many of our students don't have the time or desire to go to school for several years. We can train you for a career in broadcasting in months.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
         <h4 class="subhead">
          Job Placement Assistance
         </h4>
         <p>
          We know what prospective employers look for in applicants. We'll help you prepare your demo, polish your resumé, and prepare for job interviews.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row-fluid side-contact">
        <p>
